        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
        <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De innocentia</head>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e114">
          <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>
          ¶ De innocentia. Rubrica. 4
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e119">
          <lb ed="#V" n="22"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e116">IOb histo. c. 22.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e123">Saluabitur
            <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>innocens.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e129">
          <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e128">¶ Psalmista 36 psalmus</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e133">Custodi 
            in<lb ed="#V" n="25" break="no"/>nocentiam et vide equitatem.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e140"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e139">/ psalmus. 83</ref>
          <lb ed="#V" n="26"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e142">Non priuabit bonis eos: qui ambulant in
            <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>inocentia dominus virtutum.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e150">
          <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e153">¶ Tobias. c. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e154">Quod ab alio odis fieri tibi:
            <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>inde ne alteri tum aliquandam facias.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e160">
          <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e165">¶ Uirgilius eneide li. 7.ante medium:</ref>  <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e164">Mille
            <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>nocendi artes.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e170">
          <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e177">¶ Tullius tusculanarum questionum li. 3</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e174" source="http://scta.info/resource/ctd99a-cuh77a-d1e168@74-82">
            In<lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>nocentia est affectio talis animi quae noceat nemi.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e180">
          <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e189">¶ Ouidius de arte amandi li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e184">Fraus absit
            <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>vacuas credis habere manus.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e190">
          <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e201">¶ Quintilianus declam. 12 declam.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e194">Male
            <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>heret ibi nocentia: vbi in potestate est 
            secre<lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>tum scelus.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e203">
          <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e216">¶ Mattheus in euang. c. 27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e207">Dixit iudeis pi
            <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>latus: quid faciam de iesu qui dicitur christus. 
            Di<lb ed="#V" n="41" break="no"/>cunt omnes: crucifigatur. Ait illis pilatus: Quid
            <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>enim mali fecit: At illi magis clamabant 
            di<lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>centes: crucifigatur. Uidens autem pilatus quia
            <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>nil proficeret: sed magis tumultus fieret: 
            ac<lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>cepta aqua lauit manus suas coram populo: <!--79.xml-->
            <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
            <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>dicens: Innocens ego sum a sanguine iusti
            <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>huius: vos videritis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e232">
          <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e247">¶ Seneca tragediarum in edipo. c. 14. et finali</ref>
          <lb ed="#V" n="49"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e236">Nemo fit fato nocens. In hercule hetheo.
            <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>c. 8. Haud est nocens quicuque non sponte est 
            no<lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>cens.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e246"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e261">/ Idem epistolarum ad lucillum lib.
          <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>18. e. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e248">Securitatis magna portio est: nihil
            <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>inique facere.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e256">
          <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e276">¶ Lex diges. ti. de operis noui nunci. li. de 
            pupil<lb ed="#V" n="55" break="no"/>lo. §. si plurium.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e260">Non debet nocere factum 
              alte<lb ed="#V" n="56" break="no"/>rius: ei qui nihil fecit.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e268"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e289">/ Tit. de aqua plu. ar.
          <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>l. i. §. item ait:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e270">Aquam prodesse sibi vnusquisque
            <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>dum alii non nocet nec prohibetur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e278"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e302">/ Ti. de 
          iniu<lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>riis. l. iniuriarum. §. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e280">Iuris executio non ha
            <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>bet iniuriam.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e289">
          <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e318">¶ Marcialis cocus li. vndique suscepto. c. 2.</ref>
          <lb ed="#V" n="62"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e293">Te video solum dum possis aule nocere:
            <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>Nec prodesse tamen: sed petis vt noceas.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e301">
          <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e332">¶ Auctor li. formule honeste vite. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e305">
            Ama<lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>bis deum: si illum in hoc imitabis vt velis 
            omni<lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>bus prodesse nulli nocere: et tunc te iustum virum
            <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>appellabunt omnes: sequentur venerabuntur et dili
            <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>gent: sicque merito iustus appellaberis. 
            Iu<lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>stus vt sis non solum non nocebis: sed etiam
            <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>nocentes prohibebis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e322">
          <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e355">¶ Ambrosius de officiis li. 2. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e326">Uitam beatam
            <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>efficiunt tranquillitas conscientie et securitas
            <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>innocentie.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e334"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e367">/ Li. 3. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e336">Non latebra sapienti
          <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>spes impunitatis est: sed innocentia.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e342">
          <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e379">¶ Cecilius firmianus de beata vita libro. 3</ref>
          <lb ed="#V" n="76"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e346">Inter summas hominis virtutes innocentia 
            nu<lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>meratur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e354"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e391">/ Li. 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e356">In hoc iustitie summa 
          consi<lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>stit: vt non facias alteri quicquid ipsi ab 
          al<lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>tero pati nolis.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e365">
          <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e406">¶ Augustinus in epig. prosper. emp. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e369">
            Inno<lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>centia vera est: que nec sibi nec alteri nocet.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e375">
          <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e418">/ Emp. 75.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e379">Parum est nemini nocere: nisi
            <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>studeatur multis prodeste.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e385">
          <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e430">¶ Prosper sub vlt. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e389">Insontem vitam pacis 
            a<lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>mator agit.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e395">
          <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e442">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 6. c. 16.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e399">Innocentia
            <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>cuncta commendat.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e405"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e452">/ Li. 9. e. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e407">Uix audet 
          quis<lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>que in illos excedere: in quibus culpas non 
          po<lb ed="#V" n="89" break="no"/>test inuenire.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e415"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e464">/ Epistola. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e417">Honesta sunt lucra
          <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>per que nemo leditur.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e424"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e475">/ Epistola. 10.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e426">Nullum le <!--80.xml-->
          <pb ed="#V" n="27-r"/>
          <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
          <lb ed="#V" n="1" break="no"/>dit obseruata iustitia.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e438"> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e491">/ Li. 11. e. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e440">In qua
          <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>parte habet homo proficere: si innocentiam 
          pro<lb ed="#V" n="3" break="no"/>batus fuerit amisisse.</quote>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-d1e448">
          <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>
          <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e505">¶ Baldo. 32. fabula:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e452">In te quicquid odis 
            fie<lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>ri molumine quo vis. Cuilibet arte mali
            <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>caueas inferre sodali.</quote>
          <lb ed="#V" n="7"/> <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Rd1e516">Bernardus li. de improbatione vitiorum. c. 3</ref>
          <lb ed="#V" n="8"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19953-Qd1e521">Uir sapiens prodesse cupit nec ledere quemquam
            <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>Mitibus et gratis: nemo nocere solet.</quote>
        </p>
      </div>
